Enum Sprite.ID

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Sprite.ID>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Enclosing class:
    Sprite

    public static enum Sprite.ID
extends java.lang.Enum<Sprite.ID>
    Houses all Sprites' info. This is the only public way to represent a Sprite.
